{"tid":529314,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣令自己咩都唔諗就去做","createTime":"2018-01-14T16:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T22:11:23.000Z","uid":87428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1882fb6a02b3822244f23d7069e35aa6cfb19f22","tid":529314,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"以前細個俾老豆老母叫我<br />\n做咩都諗後果<br />\n<br />\n慢慢搞到我做咩都諗 做唔做到<br />\n做任何事都衡量成唔成功<br />\n我好驚付出左時間 （兩三年青春）<br />\n回報同付出唔成正比<br />\n最後得個吉 仲要俾兩老俾說話自己聽<br />\n搞到我現在成個廢青咁 <br />\n有咩都要問下佢地意見先<br />\n<br />\n有時諗 堆名人 偉人佢做每一件事之前有沒<br />\n算過 度過 有幾大機會成功？"},{"pid":"e86f73c7c07d25f38024ea79d441e03d6b7556cb","tid":529314,"uid":87428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T17:08:01.000Z","msg":"我係個種做又後悔 唔做又後悔<br />\n做唔到又驚 做到又擔心 之後發生咩事"},{"pid":"7ca2aa7a3b54f541b2615934ee8b72cf61154ee0","tid":529314,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"有時諗做唔做到某件事 真係可以做份計畫書俾自己睇"},{"pid":"901a3f8f04f830c28df735f75788ee592f22c40b","tid":529314,"uid":139225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T17:15:02.000Z","msg":"人就得一世<br />\n依家唔試 下世未必有得試<br />\n人 點都係會死<br />\n而做每件事 最嚴重既後果都係死<br />\n仲有咩好驚"},{"pid":"e7ec6b5a591a2e778802c7c4d573511eda992341","tid":529314,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"咁你去廁所會唔會諗呀<br />\n咪當係生理需要囉"},{"pid":"21e376ff3e5f570486f27c345b90fd173aac1897","tid":529314,"uid":120911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T17:50:15.000Z","msg":"試下調轉黎諗如果唔做會點<br />\n咁會比較convince 到自己"},{"pid":"760712a9e739f879d8d57ae726430f2d5dcd5f65","tid":529314,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e376ff3e5f570486f27c345b90fd173aac1897","tid":529314,"uid":120911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T17:50:15.000Z","msg":"試下調轉黎諗如果唔做會點<br />\n咁會比較convince 到自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T17:59:47.000Z","msg":"唔做會唔開心 同埋抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab53ee3de6da43ad8bfd27a09f18c8ab5050c2f","tid":529314,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:00:26.000Z","msg":"老套d講句<br />\n做左未必會成功<br />\n但唔做就一定唔會成功<br />\n其實應該係怕失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a958e48eacdf54ae853e89d550dbf89cff5bb0aa","tid":529314,"uid":38033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:11:23.000Z","msg":"同巴打你一樣，fg 見左好多次面試都fail, 就黎唔想apply<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}